# Pull Request Size

- Excluding `lock file` changes, each `Pull Request` should usually stay around `300` changed lines.
- Apply the same size target to the initial `Pull Request`.
- If a change would clearly exceed that target, split setup, scaffolding, and follow-up work into separate `Pull Request`s.
- When planning work, prefer small `Pull Request`s that are easy to review.
